replyContent: Thanks for the feedback. ICU Trials doesn't include "all" critical care trials. Instead, the app provides brief summaries of some of the most important or most discussed trials. replyContent: Thanks for the feedback. New trial updates are published every 4-6 months -- there are currently almost 150 trials in the database. ICU Trials catalogs the most landmark publications over the past several decades - it isn't designed to serve as a repository for the most recent publications in critical care medicine.
